feat(mcp): add template resources, pattern catalog, and view composition tools

Phase 1 - Component template resources:
- sherpa://template/{tagName} resource serves raw HTML templates (53 resources)
- query_component now includes available template IDs in response
- generate_component accepts optional templateId parameter with validation

Phase 2 - Pattern catalog:
- patterns/layouts/ - 5 layout patterns: app-shell, dashboard-grid, detail-view, list-view, settings-form
- patterns/feedback/ - 3 feedback patterns: empty-state, confirmation-dialog, loading-state
- HTML-native metadata via data-pattern-* attributes on template elements
- scripts/extract-pattern-index.js generates patterns/index.json
- npm run patterns script added; build script updated

Phase 3 - MCP server pattern tools:
- list_patterns - browse patterns by category
- get_pattern - retrieve full pattern HTML
- compose_view - combine layout pattern + component API refs
- sherpa://pattern/{patternId} resource for pattern HTML (8 resources)
- build_ui prompt enhanced with layoutPattern arg + pattern summary
- README updated: 8 tools, 120 resources, new architecture diagram
